              </div>
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-md flex flex-col items-start">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h2l1 2h13" /></svg>Detailed Candidate Reports</h3>
